# BaseResponse

This type defines the fields for any warning error messages.

## Properties

Name | Type | Description | Notes
------------ | ------------- | ------------- | -------------
**warnings** | [**List[Error]**](Error.md) | The container for any warning error messages generated by the request. Warnings are not fatal in that they do not prevent the call from running and returning a response, but they should be reviewed to ensure your requests are returning the responses you expect. | [optional]
